1</biblScope> </bibl>; but of a medical treatise, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">popular,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.551</biblScope> </bibl> (<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"comp\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Comp.\">Comp.</a></gram> </gramGrp>). </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n110858.5\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φιλάνθρωπα, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τά</gen>,</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">concessions, grants, privileges, immunities</tr_>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OGI\">OGI</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">221.14</biblScope> </bibl> (Ilium, <date TEIform=\"date\">iii B. C.</date>), <bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,P.Cair.Zen.:37:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PCair.Zen.\">PCair.Zen.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">37.11</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii B. C.)</date>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ SIG\">SIG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">548.3</biblScope> </bibl> (Delph., <date TEIform=\"date\">iii B. C.</date>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:26:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.26.8</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"http://www.trismegistos.org/text/3563\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ UPZ\">UPZ</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">162v 22</biblScope></bibl>, al. <date TEIform=\"date\">(ii B. C.)</date>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"ti